<i>adjective</i>: 흥겹다 [흥ː겹따] <i>adverb</i>: 명랑히 [명낭히] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>adjective</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>흥겹다 [흥ː겹따]</dt><br>
<dd>happy; joyful; merrily</dd><br>
<dd>흥이 나서 기분이 좋고 즐겁다.</dd><br>
<dd>Feeling good and joyful out of excitement.</dd><br>
</li>
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>명랑히 [명낭히]</dt><br>
<dd>1. radiantly</dd><br>
<dd>흐린 데 없이 밝고 환하게.</dd><br>
<dd>Shiningly and brightly without cloudiness.</dd><br>
<dd>2. merrily</dd><br>
<dd>유쾌하고 활발하게.</dd><br>
<dd>In a cheerful and outgoing manner.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>